.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
City: colone, prague, marseilles, venice
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, photography, fishing, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to prague is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| City   | colone  | venice   | marseilles     | prague |
| Hobby   | fishing  | skydiving      | cooking        | photography     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

