.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, family, spy, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
City: hannover, san-francisco, hamburg, berlin
1. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
8. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | fantasy   | spy | family |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| City     | san-francisco | hannover        | berlin       | hamburg  |

