.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, may, april, october
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, sudoku, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, iced-tea, mirinda
1. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday    | april   | october      | may       | september |
| Hobby   | camping | woodworking | sudoku     | fishing |
| Beverage     | mirinda     | juice  | hot-chocolate | iced-tea |

