.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, cricket, baseball, volleyball
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
4 different games are played: snooker, canasta, whist, backgammon
1. the person playing whist is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person playing canasta is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person playing snooker##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
5. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1
8. the person playing whist is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Sport      | baseball   | volleyball          | cricket | sailing        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | martial-arts | time-travel   | comedy     |
| Game           | snooker | canasta         | backgammon         | whist |

