.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, collecting, drawing, singing
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, boat, taxi, subway
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the person driving the taxi is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking 7up is between the person driving the tram and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
7. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | chess      | drawing       | singing    |
| Transport           | boat  | taxi  | subway | tram |
| Beverage   | soy-milk      | hot-chocolate | 7up         | lemonade    |

