.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, cooking, drawing, dancing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, swisher, cain, davidoff
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, skiing, weightlifting
1. the baccarat-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
8. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
9. the davidoff-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Hobby   | cooking         | skydiving  | drawing     | dancing         |
| Cigar        | davidoff | swisher | baccarat | cain         |
| Sport      | rugby         | skiing  | ice-hockey   | weightlifting |

