.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, november, october, february
House: cape-cod, craftsman, farmhouse, modern
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, lizard, mouse
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 2. the cape-cod house is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the farmhouse house is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the modern house is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 9. the craftsman house is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in october##2
10. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | may  | october    | november | february    |
| House   | cape-cod | farmhouse | craftsman  | modern |
| Pet           | lizard   | mouse    | dog        | horse   |

