.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, adventure, drama
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, dahlia, zinnia, sunflower
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
4. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
6. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| Movie-Genre           | drama | documentary | martial-arts   | adventure |
| Flower   | dahlia         | rose     | sunflower     | zinnia |

