1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
3. the modern house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the townhouse house is between the person who's birthday is in october and the victorian house##2
6. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
7. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lime    | cherry  | peach  | avocado |
| Birthday   | october | march | september | january |
| House   | craftsman    | townhouse     | victorian    | modern |

