.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, camping, puzzles, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, handball, skiing, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is handball is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is badminton##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | coffee  | sprite    |
| Hobby   | puzzles   | camping | dancing | sudoku |
| Sport           | ice-hockey      | skiing       | handball   | badminton      |

