.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, frog, hedgehog, ferret
City: berlin, san-francisco, miami, marseilles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person traveling to berlin##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Pet         | goat    | hedgehog | frog  | ferret  |
| City   | miami | san-francisco       | marseilles | berlin |
| Sport         | handball   | cycling      | lacrosse | golf       |

