.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bluemaster, davidoff, fonseca
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, cherry, cucumber, apricot
1. the person eating cherry is in an even position##4
2. the person eating cherry is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the person drinking cola is the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the tiparillo-smoker is the person eating cherry##1
7. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person eating apricot is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Cigar   | fonseca | tiparillo      | bluemaster | davidoff |
| Food           | cucumber   | cherry  | nectarine     | apricot |

