The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, swimming, water-polo
4 different games are played: go, scrabble, bridge, chess
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
3. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
5. the dannemann-smoker is between the person playing scrabble and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the person playing go is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar    | alhambra    | dannemann     | bluemaster    | havana        |
| Sport       | swimming   | baseball | surfing | water-polo |
| Game   | chess | bridge      | scrabble    | go   |

