1. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Birthday    | june    | may    | november  | august |
| Hobby   | reading | board-games | baking | hiking      |
| City     | san-francisco   | nizza        | paris   | new-york       |

 